description: Fluffy purchased a parrot at the MeanBitches Store that turned out to be a dead parrot. After being told “no refunds”, he asked to register a complaint and that’s when he meets Sofia Rose, the MeanBitches Complaint Department. Sofia hates whiney wimps so she tosses him like a ragdoll onto the couch and squashes him like an insect! She humiliates and degrades him and turns him into her bitch slave! HOT HUGE ASS WORSHIP, FOOT WORSHIP, FACESITTING, AND MORE!
title: The Complaint Department
